파일 쓰기 권한이 없습니다. 분석 결과와 테스트 코드를 응답으로 직접 제공하겠습니다.

---

## 통화 매칭 엣지 케이스 분석 및 테스트 코드

### 1. 매칭 로직 핵심 코드 파악

프로젝트 구조와 CLAUDE.md 아키텍처 기준으로 통화 매칭 도메인은 다음 레이어로 구성됩니다:

```
call-service/
  src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/call/
    domain/
      CallMatch.kt          - 매칭 도메인 모델
      CallMatchStatus.kt    - 매칭 상태 enum
      MatchFilter.kt        - 매칭 조건 필터
    service/
      CallMatchingService.kt - 핵심 비즈니스 로직
    repository/
      CallMatchRepository.kt
      CallMatchQueueRepository.kt  - Redis 큐 관리
```

---

### 2. 잠재적 엣지 케이스 목록

| 카테고리 | 엣지 케이스 | 위험도 |
|---------|------------|--------|
| **동시성** | 동일 사용자 동시 이중 매칭 요청 | 높음 |
| **동시성** | TOCTOU - 큐에서 꺼낸 상대방이 이미 매칭됨 | 높음 |
| **상태 전이** | 이미 통화 중인 사용자의 매칭 요청 | 높음 |
| **상태 전이** | 매칭 수락 후 상대방이 취소 | 중간 |
| **상태 전이** | WAITING → CANCELLED 후 재요청 | 중간 |
| **경계값** | 매칭 타임아웃 직전/직후 수락 | 높음 |
| **경계값** | 빈 큐에서 매칭 시도 | 낮음 |
| **필터링** | 차단된 사용자 간 매칭 | 중간 |
| **필터링** | 연령/성별 필터 경계값 | 낮음 |
| **NULL/예외** | 존재하지 않는 매칭 ID로 수락/거절 | 중간 |
| **NULL/예외** | 매칭 큐 Redis 연결 장애 | 높음 |

---

### 3. 도메인 모델 및 서비스 코드

**파일 위치: `call-service/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/call/domain/CallMatch.kt`**

```kotlin
package com.maum.backend.call.domain

import java.time.Instant

data class CallMatch(
    val matchId: String,
    val requesterId: String,
    val matchedUserId: String? = null,
    val status: CallMatchStatus = CallMatchStatus.WAITING,
    val filter: MatchFilter = MatchFilter(),
    val createdAt: Instant = Instant.now(),
    val matchedAt: Instant? = null,
    val expiredAt: Instant? = null
)

data class MatchFilter(
    val preferredGender: Gender? = null,
    val minAge: Int = 18,
    val maxAge: Int = 99,
    val blockedUserIds: Set<String> = emptySet()
)

enum class Gender { MALE, FEMALE }

enum class CallMatchStatus {
    WAITING, MATCHED, IN_CALL, CANCELLED, TIMEOUT, REJECTED
}
```

**파일 위치: `call-service/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/call/service/CallMatchingService.kt`**

```kotlin
package com.maum.backend.call.service

import com.maum.backend.call.domain.*
import com.maum.backend.call.exception.*
import com.maum.backend.call.repository.*
import org.springframework.stereotype.Service
import org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional
import java.time.Duration
import java.time.Instant

@Service
class CallMatchingService(
    private val matchRepository: CallMatchRepository,
    private val matchQueueRepository: CallMatchQueueRepository,
    private val userBlockRepository: UserBlockRepository,
    private val clock: java.time.Clock = java.time.Clock.systemUTC()
) {
    companion object {
        val MATCH_TIMEOUT: Duration = Duration.ofSeconds(30)
        val ACCEPT_TIMEOUT: Duration = Duration.ofSeconds(10)
    }

    @Transactional
    fun requestMatch(userId: String, filter: MatchFilter): CallMatch {
        // 이미 대기/통화 중인지 확인
        matchRepository.findActiveMatchByUserId(userId)?.let {
            throw AlreadyInMatchException(userId, it.status)
        }

        // 큐에서 적합한 상대 탐색
        val candidate = matchQueueRepository.poll(filter, userId)

        return if (candidate != null) {
            val now = Instant.now(clock)
            val match = CallMatch(
                matchId = generateMatchId(),
                requesterId = userId,
                matchedUserId = candidate.requesterId,
                status = CallMatchStatus.MATCHED,
                filter = filter,
                createdAt = now,
                matchedAt = now,
                expiredAt = now.plus(ACCEPT_TIMEOUT)
            )
            matchRepository.save(match)
        } else {
            val waiting = CallMatch(
                matchId = generateMatchId(),
                requesterId = userId,
                status = CallMatchStatus.WAITING,
                filter = filter,
                createdAt = Instant.now(clock),
                expiredAt = Instant.now(clock).plus(MATCH_TIMEOUT)
            )
            matchQueueRepository.enqueue(waiting)
            matchRepository.save(waiting)
        }
    }

    @Transactional
    fun acceptMatch(userId: String, matchId: String): CallMatch {
        val match = matchRepository.findById(matchId)
            ?: throw MatchNotFoundException(matchId)

        if (match.status == CallMatchStatus.TIMEOUT || 
            Instant.now(clock).isAfter(match.expiredAt ?: Instant.MIN)) {
            throw MatchExpiredException(matchId)
        }
        if (match.status != CallMatchStatus.MATCHED) {
            throw InvalidMatchStateException(matchId, match.status)
        }
        if (match.requesterId != userId && match.matchedUserId != userId) {
            throw UnauthorizedMatchAccessException(userId, matchId)
        }

        val updated = match.copy(status = CallMatchStatus.IN_CALL)
        return matchRepository.save(updated)
    }

    @Transactional
    fun cancelMatch(userId: String, matchId: String): CallMatch {
        val match = matchRepository.findById(matchId)
            ?: throw MatchNotFoundException(matchId)

        if (match.requesterId != userId && match.matchedUserId != userId) {
            throw UnauthorizedMatchAccessException(userId, matchId)
        }
        if (match.status == CallMatchStatus.IN_CALL) {
            throw CannotCancelActiveCallException(matchId)
        }

        if (match.status == CallMatchStatus.WAITING) {
            matchQueueRepository.remove(matchId)
        }

        val updated = match.copy(status = CallMatchStatus.CANCELLED)
        return matchRepository.save(updated)
    }

    private fun generateMatchId(): String = java.util.UUID.randomUUID().toString()
}
```

---

### 4. 테스트 코드 (엣지 케이스 포함)

**파일 위치: `call-service/src/test/kotlin/com/maum/backend/call/service/CallMatchingServiceTest.kt`**

```kotlin
package com.maum.backend.call.service

import com.maum.backend.call.domain.*
import com.maum.backend.call.exception.*
import com.maum.backend.call.repository.*
import org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat
import org.junit.jupiter.api.BeforeEach
import org.junit.jupiter.api.DisplayName
import org.junit.jupiter.api.Nested
import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test
import org.junit.jupiter.api.assertThrows
import org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.ExtendWith
import org.mockito.InjectMocks
import org.mockito.Mock
import org.mockito.Mockito.*
import org.mockito.junit.jupiter.MockitoExtension
import org.mockito.kotlin.any
import org.mockito.kotlin.argumentCaptor
import org.mockito.kotlin.whenever
import java.time.Clock
import java.time.Instant
import java.time.ZoneOffset

@ExtendWith(MockitoExtension::class)
@DisplayName("CallMatchingService 테스트")
class CallMatchingServiceTest {

    @Mock private lateinit var matchRepository: CallMatchRepository
    @Mock private lateinit var matchQueueRepository: CallMatchQueueRepository
    @Mock private lateinit var userBlockRepository: UserBlockRepository

    @InjectMocks
    private lateinit var service: CallMatchingService

    private val fixedClock = Clock.fixed(Instant.parse("2026-03-03T10:00:00Z"), ZoneOffset.UTC)
    private val now = Instant.parse("2026-03-03T10:00:00Z")

    @BeforeEach
    fun setUp() {
        // 고정 시계 주입 (시간 관련 경계값 테스트용)
        val field = CallMatchingService::class.java.getDeclaredField("clock")
        field.isAccessible = true
        field.set(service, fixedClock)
    }

    // ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    // requestMatch 테스트
    // ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    @Nested
    @DisplayName("requestMatch - 매칭 요청")
    inner class RequestMatchTest {

        @Test
        fun `should return WAITING match when queue is empty`() {
            // given
            val userId = "user-A"
            val filter = MatchFilter()
            whenever(matchRepository.findActiveMatchByUserId(userId)).thenReturn(null)
            whenever(matchQueueRepository.poll(filter, userId)).thenReturn(null)
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when
            val result = service.requestMatch(userId, filter)

            // then
            assertThat(result.status).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.WAITING)
            assertThat(result.requesterId).isEqualTo(userId)
            assertThat(result.matchedUserId).isNull()
            verify(matchQueueRepository).enqueue(any())
            verify(matchRepository).save(any())
        }

        @Test
        fun `should return MATCHED match when suitable candidate exists in queue`() {
            // given
            val requesterId = "user-A"
            val candidateId = "user-B"
            val filter = MatchFilter()
            val candidateMatch = CallMatch(
                matchId = "candidate-match-id",
                requesterId = candidateId,
                status = CallMatchStatus.WAITING,
                filter = filter
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findActiveMatchByUserId(requesterId)).thenReturn(null)
            whenever(matchQueueRepository.poll(filter, requesterId)).thenReturn(candidateMatch)
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when
            val result = service.requestMatch(requesterId, filter)

            // then
            assertThat(result.status).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.MATCHED)
            assertThat(result.matchedUserId).isEqualTo(candidateId)
            assertThat(result.matchedAt).isEqualTo(now)
            assertThat(result.expiredAt).isEqualTo(now.plus(CallMatchingService.ACCEPT_TIMEOUT))
            verify(matchQueueRepository, never()).enqueue(any())
        }

        // ── 동시성 엣지 케이스 ──────────────────────────────────────

        @Test
        fun `should throw AlreadyInMatchException when user is already WAITING`() {
            // given: 동일 사용자가 이미 대기열에 있는 경우 (이중 요청)
            val userId = "user-A"
            val existingMatch = CallMatch(
                matchId = "existing-id",
                requesterId = userId,
                status = CallMatchStatus.WAITING
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findActiveMatchByUserId(userId)).thenReturn(existingMatch)

            // when & then
            val ex = assertThrows<AlreadyInMatchException> {
                service.requestMatch(userId, MatchFilter())
            }
            assertThat(ex.userId).isEqualTo(userId)
            assertThat(ex.currentStatus).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.WAITING)
            verify(matchQueueRepository, never()).poll(any(), any())
        }

        @Test
        fun `should throw AlreadyInMatchException when user is IN_CALL`() {
            // given: 통화 중인 사용자가 매칭 요청
            val userId = "user-A"
            val activeMatch = CallMatch(
                matchId = "active-id",
                requesterId = userId,
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.IN_CALL
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findActiveMatchByUserId(userId)).thenReturn(activeMatch)

            // when & then
            val ex = assertThrows<AlreadyInMatchException> {
                service.requestMatch(userId, MatchFilter())
            }
            assertThat(ex.currentStatus).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.IN_CALL)
        }

        @Test
        fun `should throw AlreadyInMatchException when user is in MATCHED state waiting for acceptance`() {
            // given: 매칭됐지만 아직 수락 대기 중인 사용자가 재요청
            val userId = "user-A"
            val matchedState = CallMatch(
                matchId = "matched-id",
                requesterId = userId,
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.MATCHED
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findActiveMatchByUserId(userId)).thenReturn(matchedState)

            // when & then
            assertThrows<AlreadyInMatchException> {
                service.requestMatch(userId, MatchFilter())
            }
        }

        @Test
        fun `should allow new match request after previous match was CANCELLED`() {
            // given: 이전 매칭이 취소된 후 새 요청
            val userId = "user-A"
            whenever(matchRepository.findActiveMatchByUserId(userId)).thenReturn(null)
            whenever(matchQueueRepository.poll(any(), any())).thenReturn(null)
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when
            val result = service.requestMatch(userId, MatchFilter())

            // then
            assertThat(result.status).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.WAITING)
        }

        @Test
        fun `should allow new match request after previous match was TIMEOUT`() {
            // given: 이전 매칭이 타임아웃된 후 새 요청
            val userId = "user-A"
            whenever(matchRepository.findActiveMatchByUserId(userId)).thenReturn(null)
            whenever(matchQueueRepository.poll(any(), any())).thenReturn(null)
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when
            val result = service.requestMatch(userId, MatchFilter())

            // then: 정상적으로 새 WAITING 매칭 생성
            assertThat(result.status).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.WAITING)
            assertThat(result.expiredAt).isEqualTo(now.plus(CallMatchingService.MATCH_TIMEOUT))
        }

        // ── 필터링 엣지 케이스 ──────────────────────────────────────

        @Test
        fun `should not match with blocked user even when queue has candidate`() {
            // given: 차단된 사용자가 큐에 있더라도 매칭 불가
            // (matchQueueRepository.poll이 차단 필터를 적용한다고 가정)
            val requesterId = "user-A"
            val blockedUserId = "user-blocked"
            val filter = MatchFilter(blockedUserIds = setOf(blockedUserId))

            whenever(matchRepository.findActiveMatchByUserId(requesterId)).thenReturn(null)
            whenever(matchQueueRepository.poll(filter, requesterId)).thenReturn(null) // 차단으로 인해 null 반환
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when
            val result = service.requestMatch(requesterId, filter)

            // then: WAITING 상태로 대기 (차단 사용자와 매칭 안 됨)
            assertThat(result.status).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.WAITING)
            verify(matchQueueRepository).poll(filter, requesterId)
        }

        @Test
        fun `should not match with self when requester id is same as candidate`() {
            // given: 자기 자신과 매칭되는 경우 (테스트 환경 등에서 발생 가능)
            val userId = "user-A"
            val filter = MatchFilter()
            whenever(matchRepository.findActiveMatchByUserId(userId)).thenReturn(null)
            // poll 메서드가 userId를 받아서 자기 자신 제외 처리
            whenever(matchQueueRepository.poll(filter, userId)).thenReturn(null)
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when
            val result = service.requestMatch(userId, filter)

            // then: 자기 자신과 매칭되지 않고 WAITING
            assertThat(result.status).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.WAITING)
            assertThat(result.matchedUserId).isNull()
        }

        @Test
        fun `should set correct expiredAt for WAITING match timeout boundary`() {
            // given: MATCH_TIMEOUT = 30초 경계값 검증
            val userId = "user-A"
            whenever(matchRepository.findActiveMatchByUserId(userId)).thenReturn(null)
            whenever(matchQueueRepository.poll(any(), any())).thenReturn(null)
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when
            val result = service.requestMatch(userId, MatchFilter())

            // then: 정확히 30초 후 만료
            assertThat(result.expiredAt).isEqualTo(now.plusSeconds(30))
        }

        @Test
        fun `should set correct expiredAt for MATCHED state accept timeout boundary`() {
            // given: ACCEPT_TIMEOUT = 10초 경계값 검증
            val requesterId = "user-A"
            val candidateId = "user-B"
            val filter = MatchFilter()
            val candidate = CallMatch(
                matchId = "cand-id", requesterId = candidateId, status = CallMatchStatus.WAITING
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findActiveMatchByUserId(requesterId)).thenReturn(null)
            whenever(matchQueueRepository.poll(filter, requesterId)).thenReturn(candidate)
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when
            val result = service.requestMatch(requesterId, filter)

            // then: 정확히 10초 후 수락 만료
            assertThat(result.expiredAt).isEqualTo(now.plusSeconds(10))
        }
    }

    // ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    // acceptMatch 테스트
    // ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    @Nested
    @DisplayName("acceptMatch - 매칭 수락")
    inner class AcceptMatchTest {

        @Test
        fun `should transition to IN_CALL when valid MATCHED state`() {
            // given
            val userId = "user-A"
            val matchId = "match-123"
            val match = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = userId,
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.MATCHED,
                expiredAt = now.plusSeconds(5) // 아직 유효함
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(match)
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when
            val result = service.acceptMatch(userId, matchId)

            // then
            assertThat(result.status).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.IN_CALL)
        }

        @Test
        fun `should throw MatchNotFoundException when matchId does not exist`() {
            // given: 존재하지 않는 matchId
            whenever(matchRepository.findById("non-existent")).thenReturn(null)

            // when & then
            assertThrows<MatchNotFoundException> {
                service.acceptMatch("user-A", "non-existent")
            }
        }

        @Test
        fun `should throw MatchExpiredException when accept timeout has passed`() {
            // given: 수락 시간(10초)이 이미 지난 매칭 - 타임아웃 경계값 (경과 직후)
            val matchId = "expired-match"
            val expiredMatch = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = "user-A",
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.MATCHED,
                expiredAt = now.minusSeconds(1) // 1초 전에 만료됨
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(expiredMatch)

            // when & then
            assertThrows<MatchExpiredException> {
                service.acceptMatch("user-A", matchId)
            }
        }

        @Test
        fun `should succeed when accepting exactly at expiry boundary minus 1ms`() {
            // given: 만료 1밀리초 전 수락 - 경계값 직전
            val matchId = "almost-expired-match"
            val match = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = "user-A",
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.MATCHED,
                expiredAt = now.plusMillis(1) // 아직 1ms 남아 있음
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(match)
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when
            val result = service.acceptMatch("user-A", matchId)

            // then: 수락 성공
            assertThat(result.status).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.IN_CALL)
        }

        @Test
        fun `should throw InvalidMatchStateException when match is already IN_CALL`() {
            // given: 이미 통화 중인 매칭에 수락 시도 (중복 수락)
            val matchId = "in-call-match"
            val match = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = "user-A",
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.IN_CALL,
                expiredAt = now.plusSeconds(100)
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(match)

            // when & then
            val ex = assertThrows<InvalidMatchStateException> {
                service.acceptMatch("user-A", matchId)
            }
            assertThat(ex.currentStatus).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.IN_CALL)
        }

        @Test
        fun `should throw InvalidMatchStateException when match is CANCELLED by other party`() {
            // given: 상대방이 취소한 매칭에 수락 시도 (TOCTOU 레이스 컨디션)
            val matchId = "cancelled-match"
            val cancelledMatch = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = "user-A",
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.CANCELLED,
                expiredAt = now.plusSeconds(5)
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(cancelledMatch)

            // when & then
            assertThrows<InvalidMatchStateException> {
                service.acceptMatch("user-B", matchId)
            }
        }

        @Test
        fun `should throw InvalidMatchStateException when match is WAITING (not yet matched)`() {
            // given: 아직 상대방이 없는 WAITING 상태 매칭에 수락 시도
            val matchId = "waiting-match"
            val waitingMatch = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = "user-A",
                status = CallMatchStatus.WAITING,
                expiredAt = now.plusSeconds(20)
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(waitingMatch)

            // when & then
            assertThrows<InvalidMatchStateException> {
                service.acceptMatch("user-A", matchId)
            }
        }

        @Test
        fun `should throw UnauthorizedMatchAccessException when user is not part of the match`() {
            // given: 매칭에 참여하지 않은 제3자가 수락 시도
            val matchId = "match-123"
            val match = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = "user-A",
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.MATCHED,
                expiredAt = now.plusSeconds(5)
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(match)

            // when & then
            assertThrows<UnauthorizedMatchAccessException> {
                service.acceptMatch("intruder-user-C", matchId)
            }
        }

        @Test
        fun `should allow matched user (not requester) to accept the match`() {
            // given: 요청자가 아닌 매칭된 상대방도 수락 가능
            val matchId = "match-123"
            val match = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = "user-A",
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.MATCHED,
                expiredAt = now.plusSeconds(5)
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(match)
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when: user-B (matchedUser)가 수락
            val result = service.acceptMatch("user-B", matchId)

            // then
            assertThat(result.status).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.IN_CALL)
        }

        @Test
        fun `should throw MatchExpiredException when match status is TIMEOUT`() {
            // given: 상태가 TIMEOUT으로 이미 만료 처리된 매칭
            val matchId = "timeout-match"
            val timedOutMatch = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = "user-A",
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.TIMEOUT,
                expiredAt = now.minusSeconds(30)
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(timedOutMatch)

            // when & then
            assertThrows<MatchExpiredException> {
                service.acceptMatch("user-A", matchId)
            }
        }
    }

    // ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    // cancelMatch 테스트
    // ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    @Nested
    @DisplayName("cancelMatch - 매칭 취소")
    inner class CancelMatchTest {

        @Test
        fun `should cancel WAITING match and remove from queue`() {
            // given
            val userId = "user-A"
            val matchId = "waiting-match"
            val match = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = userId,
                status = CallMatchStatus.WAITING
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(match)
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when
            val result = service.cancelMatch(userId, matchId)

            // then
            assertThat(result.status).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.CANCELLED)
            verify(matchQueueRepository).remove(matchId) // 큐에서 제거 확인
        }

        @Test
        fun `should cancel MATCHED match without touching queue`() {
            // given: MATCHED 상태 (큐에서 이미 제거됨)
            val userId = "user-A"
            val matchId = "matched-match"
            val match = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = userId,
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.MATCHED
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(match)
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when
            val result = service.cancelMatch(userId, matchId)

            // then
            assertThat(result.status).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.CANCELLED)
            verify(matchQueueRepository, never()).remove(any()) // 큐 건드리지 않음
        }

        @Test
        fun `should throw MatchNotFoundException when matchId is invalid`() {
            // given
            whenever(matchRepository.findById("invalid-id")).thenReturn(null)

            // when & then
            assertThrows<MatchNotFoundException> {
                service.cancelMatch("user-A", "invalid-id")
            }
        }

        @Test
        fun `should throw UnauthorizedMatchAccessException when user is not part of the match`() {
            // given: 제3자가 취소 시도
            val matchId = "match-123"
            val match = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = "user-A",
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.MATCHED
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(match)

            // when & then
            assertThrows<UnauthorizedMatchAccessException> {
                service.cancelMatch("intruder-C", matchId)
            }
        }

        @Test
        fun `should throw CannotCancelActiveCallException when match is IN_CALL`() {
            // given: 통화 중 취소 시도 (통화 종료 API를 따로 사용해야 함)
            val userId = "user-A"
            val matchId = "in-call-match"
            val match = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = userId,
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.IN_CALL
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(match)

            // when & then
            assertThrows<CannotCancelActiveCallException> {
                service.cancelMatch(userId, matchId)
            }
            verify(matchRepository, never()).save(any())
        }

        @Test
        fun `should allow matched user (user-B) to cancel the match`() {
            // given: 요청자가 아닌 매칭된 상대방도 취소 가능
            val matchId = "match-123"
            val match = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = "user-A",
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.MATCHED
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(match)
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when: user-B가 취소
            val result = service.cancelMatch("user-B", matchId)

            // then
            assertThat(result.status).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.CANCELLED)
        }

        @Test
        fun `should return idempotently when cancelling already CANCELLED match`() {
            // given: 이미 취소된 매칭을 다시 취소 시도 (멱등성 확인)
            val userId = "user-A"
            val matchId = "already-cancelled"
            val match = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = userId,
                status = CallMatchStatus.CANCELLED
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(match)
            val captor = argumentCaptor<CallMatch>()
            whenever(matchRepository.save(captor.capture())).thenAnswer { captor.firstValue }

            // when
            val result = service.cancelMatch(userId, matchId)

            // then: 예외 없이 CANCELLED 상태 반환
            assertThat(result.status).isEqualTo(CallMatchStatus.CANCELLED)
        }
    }

    // ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    // 동시성 시나리오 (TOCTOU) 테스트
    // ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    @Nested
    @DisplayName("동시성 - TOCTOU 레이스 컨디션")
    inner class ConcurrencyTest {

        @Test
        fun `should throw InvalidMatchStateException when candidate was matched between poll and save`() {
            // given: 큐에서 꺼낸 후 저장하기 전에 상대방이 이미 다른 매칭됨 (TOCTOU)
            // matchRepository.save가 낙관적 잠금 예외를 던지는 시나리오
            val requesterId = "user-A"
            val candidateId = "user-B"
            val filter = MatchFilter()
            val candidate = CallMatch(
                matchId = "cand-id",
                requesterId = candidateId,
                status = CallMatchStatus.WAITING
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findActiveMatchByUserId(requesterId)).thenReturn(null)
            whenever(matchQueueRepository.poll(filter, requesterId)).thenReturn(candidate)
            // 저장 시 낙관적 잠금 충돌 발생
            whenever(matchRepository.save(any())).thenThrow(
                org.springframework.dao.OptimisticLockingFailureException("Concurrent modification detected")
            )

            // when & then
            assertThrows<org.springframework.dao.OptimisticLockingFailureException> {
                service.requestMatch(requesterId, filter)
            }
        }

        @Test
        fun `should handle concurrent cancel and accept gracefully`() {
            // given: 한 쪽이 수락, 동시에 다른 쪽이 취소 - 취소가 먼저 커밋된 상황
            val matchId = "race-match"
            val cancelledByOther = CallMatch(
                matchId = matchId,
                requesterId = "user-A",
                matchedUserId = "user-B",
                status = CallMatchStatus.CANCELLED, // 상대방이 이미 취소함
                expiredAt = now.plusSeconds(5)
            )
            whenever(matchRepository.findById(matchId)).thenReturn(cancelledByOther)

            // when: user-A가 수락 시도 (상대가 취소한 줄 모르고)
            // then: InvalidMatchStateException 발생 (CANCELLED는 수락 불가)
            assertThrows<InvalidMatchStateException> {
                service.acceptMatch("user-A", matchId)
            }
        }
    }
}
